VEHICLES

Certain areas of the game contain rideable vehicles such as hover cycles,
APCs, and the EX-5 Behemoth giant robot.

BASIC VEHICLE COMMANDS
  enter <vehicle>       board a vehicle in the room
  exit                  leave your current vehicle
  drive <direction>     pilot the vehicle in a direction (when powered)

HOVER CYCLE
  The hover cycle in Monument Square is available to all players.
  Enter it, then use compass directions to drive it.
  The cycle can move through vehicle-accessible areas.

EX-5 BEHEMOTH
  The EX-5 is a massive giant robot found in the buried chamber beneath
  the Splynn Dimensional Market.  Access the market, dig through the
  ground patch, then enter the underground chamber.
  Inside the EX-5:
    power on            starts the EX-5's systems
    power off           shuts it down
    status              shows current fuel and condition
    north/south/etc     pilots the machine while powered

NOTES
  Vehicles require fuel.  The EX-5 can be refueled at the fuel pump in
  the buried chamber.
  Not all rooms are vehicle-accessible.  Cramped interiors block vehicle
  movement.

